  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK807">
<l>aḻivanta ceyyiṉu maṉpaṟā raṉpiṉ </l>
<l>vaḻivanta kēṇmai yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have (long) stood in the path of affection will not give it up even if their friends cause (them) their ruin.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
